<i>noun</i>: 햇살 [해쌀/핻쌀], 햇빛 [해삗/핻삗], 햇볕 [해뼏/핻뼏], 일광 [일광], 양기 [양기], 볕 [볃] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>햇살 [해쌀/핻쌀]</dt><br>
<dd>sunlight; sunshine</dd><br>
<dd>해가 내쏘는 광선.</dd><br>
<dd>The light the sun radiates.</dd><br>
<dt>햇빛 [해삗/핻삗]</dt><br>
<dd>1. sunlight; sunbeam; sunshine</dd><br>
<dd>해의 빛.</dd><br>
<dd>Light from the sun.</dd><br>
<dd>2. seeing the light</dd><br>
<dd>(비유적으로) 세상에 알려져 칭찬받거나 이름을 날리게 되는 것.</dd><br>
<dd>(figurative) A state of becoming known to the public and receiving praise or gaining fame.</dd><br>
<dt>햇볕 [해뼏/핻뼏]</dt><br>
<dd>sunshine; sunlight</dd><br>
<dd>해가 내리쬐는 기운.</dd><br>
<dd>An effect caused by the beating sun.</dd><br>
<dt>일광 [일광]</dt><br>
<dd>sunlight; sunbeam; sunshine</dd><br>
<dd>해의 빛.</dd><br>
<dd>A light from the sun.</dd><br>
<dt>양기 [양기]</dt><br>
<dd>1. sunshine; sunlight</dd><br>
<dd>햇볕의 따뜻한 기운.</dd><br>
<dd>The warm energy of sunshine.</dd><br>
<dd>2. vitality; vigor</dd><br>
<dd>세상의 모든 것이 살아 움직이는 활발한 기운.</dd><br>
<dd>The vigorous energy coming from all living things in the world.</dd><br>
<dd>3. energy; positive energy</dd><br>
<dd>몸 안에 있는 양의 기운. 또는 남자 몸 안의 정기.</dd><br>
<dd>The energy of the positive in one's body; the vigor of a male's body.</dd><br>
<dt>볕 [볃]</dt><br>
<dd>sunshine; sunlight</dd><br>
<dd>해가 내리쬐는 뜨거운 기운.</dd><br>
<dd>Hot air caused by the beating sun.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>